name: Cleopatra - FGO
description:
Cleopatra from F/GO, all outfits.

Swimsuit sometimes gets faded lines as if it was painted on, and 3rd asc training was unable to capture the cross-laced part on the front of her dress. Main outfit has an issue with generating an entirely black top instead of one with white sleeves, so you can try to add white jacket to solve this issue, however I don't guarantee anything.

Images in preview may be from past versions! Do not expect full replication!

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: I realized that v1 was actually set to resume training off a previous failed version of the lora. V2 is completely and freshly retrained, with much sharper outputs. Unfortunately, it seems it lacks as much coherency with the dress and swimsuit, but it does gen her main outfit better than V1, so you decide if that's a good trade-off.
